36
00:02:07.248 --> 00:02:11.925
>> Yes, if you want to start writing
code from scratch, it's a huge topic,

37
00:02:11.925 --> 00:02:15.622
but we're going to use Excel's
built in macro recorder to

38
00:02:15.622 --> 00:02:17.747
