duplicating it for similar procedures.

44
00:02:35.208 --> 00:02:38.291
>> Well,
that's definitely going to be a highlight.

45
00:02:38.291 --> 00:02:40.282
So really, no charts this week?

46
00:02:40.282 --> 00:02:44.584
>> Well, not in the strict sense, but
we are going to look at sparklines,

47
00:02:44.584 --> 00:02:48.027
which are miniature charts
that sit in a single cell, and

48
00:02:48.027 --> 00:02:52.116
they allow us to quickly generate
multiple trend visualizations,

49
00:02:52.116 --> 00:02:54.867
will also be including pictures and
shapes.

50
00:02:54.867 --> 00:02:57.472
