shapes in Excel?

51
00:02:57.472 --> 00:03:02.460
>> Actually, there are loads, shapes very
useful for labels, for framing data.

52
00:03:02.460 --> 00:03:07.181
We're going to use them as macro buttons,
and they can even be linked to a cell, so

53
00:03:07.181 --> 00:03:09.800
